{"tid":498663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★HK No IT 港府IT大落後 資訊系統是逾十年前的舊貨","createTime":"2017-12-14T04:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T16:11:31.000Z","uid":19454,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"591bfc7898014f20b6fc3e6f67fd7685af21f30c","tid":498663,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:32:55.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】香港政府近年聲言致力發展創新科技，但各部門向市民提供服務的資訊科技卻落後得驚人！其中運輸署「香港行車易」網站提供的停車場實時空置泊位資訊，被立法會議員揭發出現以小時甚至月計的「時差」。該署承認轄下停車場的進出監控系統及車牌<span style=\"color: red;\">辨認系統，已是逾十年前的舊貨色</span>，未能支援自動提供實時停車位資訊的功能，目前只是依靠停車場營辦商每小時以人手更新「香港行車易」的停車場資訊。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「一站通」仍用Java軟件</span><br />\n政府一站通網站亦同樣落後，立法會議員莫乃光發現，車主要在網上辦理車輛牌照（俗稱行車證）續證手續，必須透過該網站處理，而申請人的電腦須安裝Java才能使用有關服務。惟近年多個常用瀏覽器如Edge、Firefox及Chrome等已停止支援Java軟件，令申請人難以應用網站<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20171214/00176_055.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171214%2F00176_055.html&d=oX%2FzVSq82eT82GbXMN2w9BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=1d9fb132\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20171214/00176_055.html</a>"},{"pid":"5e2437eed04e821ce18a172da465a756a5279a5c","tid":498663,"uid":19454,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:33:15.000Z","msg":"仍用Java軟件<br />\n仍用Java軟件<br />\n仍用Java軟件<br />\n仍用Java軟件"},{"pid":"d9b07df9d2c2866f4f9332e2088acf69d9bfb84c","tid":498663,"uid":51904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:33:55.000Z","msg":"IT is free!"},{"pid":"00ef6f33e949cc7524c1f68848597565770aad0c","tid":498663,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:34:07.000Z","msg":"網上續證的手續十分繁複，申請人必須持有有效的個人或機構數碼證書，運輸署亦不接受網上逾期續證申請，政府甚至<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">建議市民親身辦理續證手續</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"473fa583ccfd1aaf7ad840da842ad4bf0c5863f8","tid":498663,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:34:18.000Z","msg":"活在不同時空的香港政府"},{"pid":"09fe628bc23e3b221aa0719cfd05b2a4e43b3a21","tid":498663,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:34:43.000Z","msg":"建議市民親身辦理續證手續<br />\n建議市民親身辦理續證手續<br />\n建議市民親身辦理續證手續<br />\n建議市民親身辦理續證手續<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNo IT anymore<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7342adeec83119f39047fcf3ace8477b1803b227","tid":498663,"uid":7760,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:36:23.000Z","msg":"遲下政府大搞新系統, IT 大把野撈!"},{"pid":"64d9eebada5cfc190dbe980432f4b42dab49c6ac","tid":498663,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5694bb2c393e7cf2b3a14b80a510ee5a59b4e747","tid":498663,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:37:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遲下政府大搞新系統, IT 大把野撈!</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新系統=市民親身辦理續證手續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f71c05ab33a906bd6e902c214e395ca19ccbeba","tid":498663,"uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:38:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遲下政府大搞新系統, IT 大把野撈!</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2014